{"id":231987,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/06/维权网-上海民众为争取诉权再到最高法院门口抗/","date":"2012-06-16T04:00:46Z","modified":"2012-06-16T04:00:46Z","title":"维权网 | 上海民众为争取诉权再到最高法院门口抗议（组图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div><span></span></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a>（维权网信息员晨晓报道）<span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13</span><span>日下午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>时，上海市各区县的部分冤民冒着炎热撑着阳伞在市高级法院门口抗议法院的司法腐败，与往日不同的是，在法院门口的便道上停放着</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>辆有“法院”字样的大型警车，几乎占据了所有的便道。冤民们无处立足，只得停留在马路边侧。大家推测法院的作法其目的是不让冤民们靠近法院。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></p>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>整个抗议活动持续</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>小时，法院没有任何人出来接待冤民，也没有警察出来干涉，期间，有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>名保安出来撕掉冤民贴在“法院”字样的大型警车上的“抗议司法腐败，法院不讲法”的标语。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>小时后，冤民们自行暂时离开。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>参与抗议的冤民们表示：下一个星期三下午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>时会继续再来抗议，坚决不放弃：“我要立案，捍卫法律，还我诉权”。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>每周三下午上海民众自发到最高法院抗议争取诉权行动自今年初开始，几个月来，不管遇到什么样的阻挠，大家都从来没有放弃过。部分冤民说：枉为人民法院，却从来不为人民申冤，凡是民告官的案子不立案，不裁定。就是立案，也是枉法裁判，财产被抢的老百姓必输无疑，我们求诉无门。法律的尊严不见了踪影，没有了公平正义，我们民告官的诉求彻底被法院剥夺。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>上海市因为强制拆迁、非法征地、医疗纠纷、司法不公、非法关押等各种行政诉讼案绝大多数都未获立案，为了争取公民的诉权，以冯正虎为代表的上海维权人士代表</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1060</span><span>户居民发起“我要立案，捍卫法律，还我诉权”的公民行动，冯正虎自今年的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">27</span><span>日</span><span>被非法囚禁在家中至今。</span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-Zz9XRGdjF-s/T9v3yM68svI/AAAAAAAAIho/zHc3bjYvMsY/s1600/1.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"215\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-Zz9XRGdjF-s/T9v3yM68svI/AAAAAAAAIho/zHc3bjYvMsY/s320/1.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-o762K1F7hjU/T9v32JSW2EI/AAAAAAAAIhw/YnlZE7OvO2o/s1600/2.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-o762K1F7hjU/T9v32JSW2EI/AAAAAAAAIhw/YnlZE7OvO2o/s320/2.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-CvozZWkvc9U/T9v36M2BOJI/AAAAAAAAIh4/zznQXOsdwRI/s1600/SAM_0175.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-CvozZWkvc9U/T9v36M2BOJI/AAAAAAAAIh4/zznQXOsdwRI/s1600/SAM_0175.JPG\" width=\"240\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-ZakwYK5DQhU/T9v3-VHuQbI/AAAAAAAAIiA/jHncRjKHVFI/s1600/SAM_0178.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-ZakwYK5DQhU/T9v3-VHuQbI/AAAAAAAAIiA/jHncRjKHVFI/s320/SAM_0178.JPG\" width=\"240\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-IWQzuHPg69o/T9v4EusnldI/AAAAAAAAIiI/ZOZK8W4-9uY/s1600/SAM_0182.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-IWQzuHPg69o/T9v4EusnldI/AAAAAAAAIiI/ZOZK8W4-9uY/s320/SAM_0182.JPG\" width=\"240\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-_Ofvc40M_Io/T9v4ISQyEVI/AAAAAAAAIiQ/WMNHpF9jHeI/s1600/SAM_0183.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-_Ofvc40M_Io/T9v4ISQyEVI/AAAAAAAAIiQ/WMNHpF9jHeI/s320/SAM_0183.JPG\" width=\"240\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-fDP5Ju5z9lU/T9v4MdWZL4I/AAAAAAAAIiY/b2Kqbra5RjM/s1600/SAM_0185.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-fDP5Ju5z9lU/T9v4MdWZL4I/AAAAAAAAIiY/b2Kqbra5RjM/s320/SAM_0185.JPG\" width=\"240\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-CpxIMIwz4c4/T9v4RQbGfDI/AAAAAAAAIig/hezGm0rJe4c/s1600/SAM_0186.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"ht